      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 3 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 16 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 4 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 16</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique must be used within 1 round of the target having missed a charge attack against you. Make a melee attack against the target that deals normal damage, and allows you to make a free trip attempt against the target without provoking an attack of opportunity.</p>\n\n\n\n",
